divs: Sighting DetailsTook several photos in sequence of sky over jobsite. When uploaded to PC I discovered that there was more than one. I don't know what inspires me to take the pictures I just get a feeling and there they are. I have several from last year on my site at fdinwidy7.tripod.com and I am seeing alot of activity starting already this year over our area. Also if Don Braffit reads this I had a really weird experience while sleeping three days before. I awoke in bed and was on my side and I could not move and didn't want to move because I had a pulsating wave going through my body from head to toe but mainly along my spine. It was as if I was floating but I know I was on the bed because I had my eyes open...too strange I know and I cannot say I've ever had an abduction experience so I won't say this is one but it was strange. Also I am seeing the craft with my own eyes sometimes rather than just random photo's of the sky.
Summary: Took several photos in sequence of sky over jobsite.
